Description: A companion package and website for the guide 
    "Building a Design-Based Matching Pipeline: From Principles to Practical Implementation in R".
    It packages helper functions and example data used in the guide, provides vignettes that 
    reproduce the guide, and offers downloadable data and teaching materials.
